    <h2 class="article-title" itemprop="headline">Robert Griffin III: What I&#8217;m Thankful For</h2>
  <div class="article-sub-headline">
    <div class="article-meta">

        <ul class="article-authors">
            <li class="article-author ">
              <span class="byline"><a itemprop="author" href="http://time.com/author/robert-griffin-iii/">Robert Griffin III</a></span>
