    	<a class="time-icons time-icons-gplus social-link-gplus popup" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3599575%2Frobert-griffin-iii-redskins-thanks%2F" data-event="google+" title="Click to post this article to Google+"></a>
