/","shortlink":"http:\/\/wp.me\/p5HMd-f61q","title":"In <i>Free the Nipple<\/i> Movie, Women Go Topless for Equality","friendly_title":"In Free the Nipple Movie, Women Go Topless for Equality","post_type":"post","available":true,"time_article":true,"comments_allowed":true,"short_title":"In <i>Free the Nipple<\/i> Movie, Women Go Topless for Equality","excerpt":"\u201cSomeone is definitely getting arrested.\u201d","format":"video","time":{"pretty":"Nov. 21, 2014","published":"2014-11-21 10:39:34","updated":"2014-11-21 15:39:34","minute":"10:39 am","short":"11\/21"},"authors":[{"id":291298709,"url":"http:\/\/time.com\/author\/eliza-berman\/","name":"Eliza Berman","bio":"","short_bio":"","types":["contributor"],"twitter":"lizabeaner","twitter_url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/lizabeaner","gplus":"","fb":"","email":"","thumbnail":null,"contributor":false}],"content":"<p>Censorship matters to Lina Esco, whose new film <i>Free the Nipple<\/i> tells the story of a group of activists challenging laws by baring their chests in the streets.<\/p>\n<p>For Esco, &ldquo;It&rsquo;s not about going topless, it&rsquo;s about equality.&rdquo; The movie grew out of a <a href=\"http:\/\/www.freethenipple.com\/\">real-life campaign <\/a>that questions a country that glorifies violence in the media but <a href=\"http:\/\/content.time.com\/time\/specials\/packages\/article\/0,28804,2053230_2053229_2053225,00.html\">removes a woman <\/a>from a flight for breastfeeding her baby. As one of the fictional activists says in the trailer, &ldquo;Our sexuality has been taken away from us and is essentially being sold back to us.&rdquo;<\/p>\n<p>The movement got a jump-start when Miley Cyrus, who has faced plenty of censorship herself, tweeted a <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/MileyCyrus\/status\/410651500541902848\/photo\/1\">picture of herself<\/a> holding a fake nipple last December, accompanied by the hashtag #freethenipple. It&rsquo;s not lost on Esco that the sensationalism of a bunch of topless women can only help to spread the word about her cause. &ldquo;If I would have made a movie called &lsquo;Equality,&rsquo; and no one was going topless,&rdquo; she acknowledged to <a href=\"http:\/\/insidemovies.ew.com\/2014\/11\/19\/free-the-nipple-exclusive-trailer\/\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Entertainment Weekly<\/i><\/a>, &ldquo;nobody would be talking about it.&rdquo;<\/p>\n<p><i>Free the Nipple <\/i>hits theaters on Dec. 12.<\/p>\n<aside class=\"right-rail-module rr-share\" data-name=\"rr-share\"><span class=\"social-links\">\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-mail social-link-mail\" href=\"mailto:?subject=In%20Free%20the%20Nipple%20Movie%2C%20Women%20Go%20Topless%20for%20Equality%20%7C%20TIME&body=In%20Free%20the%20Nipple%20Movie%2C%20Women%20Go%20Topless%20for%20Equality%0A%0A%E2%80%9CSomeone%20is%20definitely%20getting%20arrested.%E2%80%9D%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598072%2Ffree-the-nipple-movie-trailer%2F\" data-event=\"email\" title=\"Click to Email this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-fb social-link-fb popup\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sharer\/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598072%2Ffree-the-nipple-movie-trailer%2F\" data-event=\"fb-share\" title=\"Click to post this article to Facebook\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f61q&text=In%20Free%20the%20Nipple%20movie%2C%20women%20go%20topless%20for%20equality&via=TIME\" data-event=\"tweet\" title=\"Click to Tweet this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup\" href=\"http:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598072%2Ffree-the-nipple-movie-trailer%2F&title=In+Free+the+Nipple+Movie%2C+Women+Go+Topless+for+Equality\" data-event=\"linkedin\" title=\"Click to post this article to LinkedIn\"><\/a>\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"time-icons time-icons-comment toggle-co