%20power%20of%20silence&via=TIME\" data-event=\"tweet\" title=\"Click to Tweet this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup\" href=\"http:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598207%2Fbill-cosby-rape-accusations-silence%2F&title=Bill+Cosby%2C+Camille+Cosby+and+the+Oppressive+Power+of+Silence\" data-event=\"linkedin\" title=\"Click to post this article to LinkedIn\"><\/a>\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"time-icons time-icons-comment toggle-comments\" data-lf-site-id=\"314099\" data-lf-article-id=\"3598207\" data-url=\"http:\/\/time.com\/3598207\/bill-cosby-rape-accusations-silence\/\" data-title=\"Bill Cosby, Camille Cosby and the Oppressive Power of Silence\" title=\"Click to view and post comments\" data-event=\"comment-click\">0<\/a>\n<\/span>\n<\/aside>","section":{"name":"Living","slug":"living","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/living\/","description":"The latest news and commentary from TIME on society, relationships, parenting, sex, psychology, aging, gender, career, women's issues, marriage, love and more"},"tag":{"name":"Opinion","slug":"time-section-opinion","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/tag\/time-section-opinion\/"},"tags":"alleged rape|Bill Cosby|Culture|Media|Opinion|women","id":3598207,"encoded_url":"http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598207%2Fbill-cosby-rape-accusations-silence%2F","encoded_shortlink":"http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f63B","encoded_title":"Bill+Cosby%2C+Camille+Cosby+and+the+Oppressive+Power+of+Silence","video":{"title":"Bill Cosby, Camille Cosby and the Oppressive Power of Silence","embed":"<div class=\"video-wrapper\" data-pos=\"7\" data-continuous=\"1\"><object id=\"bc-video-3900439492001-7\" class=\"BrightcoveExperience\"><param name=\"bgcolor\" value=\"#000000\"><param name=\"width\" value=\"100%\"><param name=\"height\" value=\"100%\"><param name=\"playerID\" value=\"1847503743001\"><param name=\"isVid\" value=\"true\"><param name=\"isUI\" value=\"true\"><param name=\"dynami